<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Tridacna_gigas.001_-_Aquarium_Finisterrae.JPG" class="image"><img alt="Shell of the giant clam (Tridacna gigas)" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Tridacna_gigas.001_-_Aquarium_Finisterrae.JPG/220px-Tridacna_gigas.001_-_Aquarium_Finisterrae.JPG" width="220" height="165" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Tridacna_gigas.001_-_Aquarium_Finisterrae.JPG/330px-Tridacna_gigas.001_-_Aquarium_Finisterrae.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Tridacna_gigas.001_-_Aquarium_Finisterrae.JPG/440px-Tridacna_gigas.001_-_Aquarium_Finisterrae.JPG 2x" /></a>
