<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Ensis_phaxoides-V.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf8/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
