<li id="cite_note-Bouchet_Rocroi__2010-117"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Bouchet_Rocroi_2010_117-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Bouchet_Rocroi_2010_117-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation Journal" id="CITEREFBouchetRocroiBielerCarter2010">Bouchet, Philippe; Rocroi, Jean-Pierre; Bieler, Rüdiger; Carter, Joseph G.; Coan, Eugene V. (2010). "Nomenclator of Bivalve Families with a Classification of Bivalve Families". <i><a href="Malacologia" title="Malacologia">Malacologia</a></i> <b>52</b> (2): 1–184. <a href="Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.4002/040.052.0201">10.4002/040.052.0201</a>.</span> <span class="plainlinks noprint" style="font-size:smaller"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Template_Cite_doi_10.4002.2F040.052.0201&action=edit&editintro=Template_Cite_doi_editintro2.php.html">edit</a></span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-T.C3.ABmkin_2010-118"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-T.C3.ABmkin_2010_118-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation Journal">I, I. (2010). "Molecular phylogeny of pearl oysters and their relatives (Mollusca, Bivalvia, Pterioidea) <a href="Open_access" title="Open access"><img alt="Open Access logo PLoS transparent.svg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg/8px-Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg.png" width="8" height="13" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg/12px-Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg/16px-Open_Access_logo_PLoS_transparent.svg.png 2x" /></a>". <i>BMC Evolutionary Biology</i> <b>10</b>: 342. <a href="Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1186/1471-2148-10-342">10.1186/1471-2148-10-342</a>.</span></span></li>
